'''綠帽'''（{{lang-en|'''Cuckservative'''}}；常缩写为'''Cuck'''，也是cuckold（[[绿帽子|绿帽子]]）的缩写）是一个用来攻击对手缺乏男子气概的侮辱性词语。美国[[另类右翼|另类右翼]]常使用'''綠帽(Cuck)'''一詞攻擊不願意支持[[白人優越主義|白人至上]]及[[反犹太主义|反猶]]的保守派<ref>{{Cite web|title=“反法”、“绿帽”：美国极端政治术语一览|url=https://cn.nytimes.com/usa/20170816/alt-left-alt-right-glossary/|access-date=2021-10-01|date=2017-08-16|last=Stack|first=Liam|work=纽约时报中文网|language=zh-hans|quote=“绿帽”是“另类右翼”用来攻击对手缺乏男性气质的侮辱词语，最早是用来攻击并不完全致力于种族主义和反犹太主义的其他保守派。}}</ref>。

Cuck 可以指出賣保守派<ref name="hotair-07-26-2015">{{cite news |last=Millard |first=Taylor |date=2015-07-26 |title=Don't believe the #cuckservative lie |url=http://hotair.com/archives/2015/07/26/dont-believe-the-cuckservative-lie/ |newspaper=Hot Air |access-date=2015-08-21 |archive-date=2015-08-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150821051051/http://hotair.com/archives/2015/07/26/dont-believe-the-cuckservative-lie/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，擁護左派價值<ref name="buzzfeed-07-28-2015">{{cite news |last=Bernstein |first=Joseph |date=2015-07-28 |title=Behind The Racist Hashtag That Is Blowing Up Twitter |url=https://www.buzzfeed.com/josephbernstein/behind-the-racist-hashtag-some-donald-trump-fans-love |newspaper=BuzzFeed |access-date=2015-08-21 |archive-date=2015-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150820012156/http://www.buzzfeed.com/josephbernstein/behind-the-racist-hashtag-some-donald-trump-fans-love |dead-url=no }}</ref>，反基督教的人<ref name="redstate-07-29-2015">{{cite news |author=[[Erick_Erickson|Erick Erickson]] |date=2015-07-29 |title="Cuckservative" is a Racist Slur and an Attack on Evangelical Christians |url=http://www.redstate.com/2015/07/29/cuckservative-is-a-racist-slur-and-an-attack-on-evangelical-christians/ |newspaper=Red State |access-date=2015-08-21 |archive-date=2015-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150820014337/http://www.redstate.com/2015/07/29/cuckservative-is-a-racist-slur-and-an-attack-on-evangelical-christians/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，與[[RINO|RINO]]（名義上的共和黨人）意思相近。

